name: RAEN-Deakin Poler Colab(Gray Crystal Frame Smoke CR-39 Polarized Lens)
description:
Raen Optics, the handmade heartfelt Southern California based brand, is proud to present the collaboration with friends, POLER Stuff, an outdoor lifestyle brand that offers camping essentials and adventure equipment. 

A natural fit for a timeless collaboration, RAEN and Poler Stuff share a keen eye for design sensibility and an adventure-bearing consumer. The collaboration has brought us three of our favorite new finishes to some of our most solid styles. Featuring polished black and grey crystal acetate with a unique metal logo applique, these frames are sure to draw in anyone with vision. The RAEN x POLER Stuff collaboration boasts Optics by Carl Zeiss polarized lenses.

• Handcrafted Zyl Acetate Frame
• Optics by Carl Zeiss CR-39 Lens offering 100% UVA/UVB protection
• Shipped with custom POLER Tent Case

Just don't go calling me at 3 in the morning asking me to come get you out of the slam after you got arrested at a Rax for threatening the manger because your roast beef sandwich was cold. They just have other stuff to do and don't have time to assimilate into our society. Its cool though cause if any of these mythical creatures showed it wouldn't be long before they would be serving you fast food, forced into freak shows, Working on bridges, Creeping people out in hospital ERs and pulling carriages in beer commercials.
